<section id="faq" class="faq-section" aria-labelledby="faq-title">
    <div class="faq-inner">
        <div class="faq-heading">
            <span class="faq-kicker">Family guidance</span>
            <h2 id="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Clear answers for families considering private household and childcare introductions in Dubai.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
            <details class="faq-item" open>
                <summary>
                    <span>How do I hire a nanny in Dubai?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Trusted Household Care helps families in Dubai identify suitable nannies through a calm, structured introduction process. Each candidate is reviewed before being introduced to your family.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>What is the difference between a nanny and a babysitter?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>A nanny usually provides ongoing childcare support and becomes part of a family&rsquo;s regular routine, while a babysitter is typically engaged for occasional or short-term childcare needs.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>Do you provide housekeepers in Dubai?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes. Families can request introductions to experienced housekeepers, household assistants, and other domestic staff depending on their household requirements.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>How are candidates screened?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Candidate profiles are reviewed through a structured selection process that may include interviews, experience verification, reference checks where available, and suitability assessment before introduction.</p>
                </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary>
                    <span>Can I request a consultation before reviewing candidates?</span>
                </summary>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes. We begin with a consultation to understand your household requirements, preferences, and expectations before recommending suitable candidates.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

